  "description": "Map of the Sofia metropolitan area (Bulgaria), including Sofia Airport and the surrounding urban region. 130k+ OSM buildings with binary building index, 1.23M residents and 552k+ jobs with demand built from Bulgarian census data, OpenStreetMap buildings and an IPF-based origin-destination model. Density-adaptive demand grid with 1 km, 500 m and 250 m cells, producing 2,793 active demand points. Commuting, student, urban mobility and special-attractor demand for Sofia Airport, major universities, hospitals, shopping centres and entertainment venues. Sofia Airport runways and taxiways. Native PMTiles basemap with water, parks and buildings.",
